---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Explorers Academy"
  description="The Weyland-Yutani Explorers Academy provides STEM education, scholarships, and mentorship to the next generation of scientists, engineers, and leaders. Over $5B donated through the Little Explorers program."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-black pt-36">
    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden border-b-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-20"></div>
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 text-center py-24">
        <div class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 clip-corner">
          CAREERS &mdash; EDUCATION
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black text-white mb-8 leading-none uppercase">
          EXPLORERS <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">ACADEMY</span>
        </h1>

        <div class="h-1 w-64 bg-[#FFC600] mx-auto mb-8"></div>

        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto uppercase tracking-wide font-mono">
          INVESTING IN THE NEXT GENERATION OF LEADERS, SCIENTISTS, AND EXPLORERS.
          BECAUSE THE FUTURE BELONGS TO THOSE WHO PREPARE FOR IT TODAY.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- MISSION -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">OUR MISSION</span>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-white mt-4 mb-6 uppercase">
              EDUCATION WITHOUT <span class="text-[#FFC600]">BOUNDARIES</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
              FOUNDED IN 2025, THE WEYLAND-YUTANI EXPLORERS ACADEMY WAS ESTABLISHED WITH A SINGULAR PURPOSE: TO PROVIDE WORLD-CLASS STEM EDUCATION TO UNDERPRIVILEGED STUDENTS REGARDLESS OF THEIR GEOGRAPHIC, ECONOMIC, OR SOCIAL CIRCUMSTANCES.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
              WHAT BEGAN AS A PILOT PROGRAM IN THREE CITIES HAS GROWN INTO THE LARGEST PRIVATE EDUCATION INITIATIVE IN HUMAN HISTORY, OPERATING ON EVERY CONTINENT AND EXTENDING TO OUR LUNAR CAMPUS.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed">
              THE ACADEMY REPRESENTS OUR MOST FUNDAMENTAL CONVICTION: THAT TALENT IS UNIVERSAL, BUT OPPORTUNITY IS NOT. WE EXIST TO CLOSE THAT GAP.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">$5B+</div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase">TOTAL EDUCATION INVESTMENT</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase">THROUGH THE LITTLE EXPLORERS PROGRAM</div>
            </div>
            <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">250K+</div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase">STUDENTS ENROLLED</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase">ACROSS ALL ACADEMY LOCATIONS</div>
            </div>
            <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">94%</div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase">GRADUATE EMPLOYMENT RATE</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase">WITHIN 6 MONTHS OF COMPLETION</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- LITTLE EXPLORERS PROGRAM -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-black border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">FLAGSHIP INITIATIVE</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">
            LITTLE <span class="text-[#FFC600]">EXPLORERS</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-wide mt-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            OUR CORNERSTONE PROGRAM PROVIDING FULL SCHOLARSHIPS, MENTORSHIP, AND CAREER PATHWAYS
            TO STUDENTS FROM UNDERSERVED COMMUNITIES WORLDWIDE.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-black text-lg font-black">1</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">SCHOLARSHIP</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">
              FULL-RIDE SCHOLARSHIPS COVERING TUITION, MATERIALS, HOUSING, AND LIVING EXPENSES FOR STUDENTS AGES 14-22. OVER 50,000 SCHOLARSHIPS AWARDED ANNUALLY ACROSS 40 COUNTRIES AND THREE OFF-WORLD LOCATIONS.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-black text-lg font-black">2</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">MENTORSHIP</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">
              EVERY ACADEMY STUDENT IS PAIRED WITH A WEYLAND-YUTANI PROFESSIONAL MENTOR. OUR 15,000+ VOLUNTEER MENTORS PROVIDE GUIDANCE ON ACADEMICS, CAREER DEVELOPMENT, AND PERSONAL GROWTH THROUGHOUT THE PROGRAM.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <span class="text-black text-lg font-black">3</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">INTERNSHIP PIPELINE</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">
              ACADEMY GRADUATES RECEIVE PRIORITY PLACEMENT IN OUR CORPORATE INTERNSHIP PROGRAM. OVER 85% OF INTERNS RECEIVE FULL-TIME OFFERS, CREATING A DIRECT PATHWAY FROM EDUCATION TO CAREER AT WEYLAND-YUTANI.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ACADEMY LOCATIONS -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">CAMPUS NETWORK</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">
            ACADEMY <span class="text-[#FFC600]">LOCATIONS</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="corp-card p-6">
            <h4 class="text-white font-black text-sm uppercase mb-2">SAN FRANCISCO</h4>
            <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs uppercase">FLAGSHIP CAMPUS</span>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-3 leading-relaxed">3,200 STUDENTS. ADJACENT TO CORPORATE HQ WITH DIRECT ACCESS TO RESEARCH LABS AND INDUSTRY PROFESSIONALS.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-6">
            <h4 class="text-white font-black text-sm uppercase mb-2">TOKYO</h4>
            <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs uppercase">ASIA-PACIFIC CAMPUS</span>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-3 leading-relaxed">2,800 STUDENTS. SPECIALIZED IN ELECTRONICS AND ROBOTICS EDUCATION WITH YUTANI HERITAGE PROGRAMS.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-6">
            <h4 class="text-white font-black text-sm uppercase mb-2">NAIROBI</h4>
            <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs uppercase">AFRICA CAMPUS</span>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-3 leading-relaxed">2,100 STUDENTS. FOCUS ON ENVIRONMENTAL SCIENCE AND SUSTAINABLE TECHNOLOGY EDUCATION.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-6">
            <h4 class="text-white font-black text-sm uppercase mb-2">SAO PAULO</h4>
            <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs uppercase">SOUTH AMERICA CAMPUS</span>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-3 leading-relaxed">1,900 STUDENTS. SPECIALIZING IN BIOLOGICAL SCIENCES AND ECOLOGICAL ENGINEERING CURRICULA.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-6">
            <h4 class="text-white font-black text-sm uppercase mb-2">MUMBAI</h4>
            <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs uppercase">SOUTH ASIA CAMPUS</span>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-3 leading-relaxed">2,500 STUDENTS. LEADING PROGRAMS IN SOFTWARE ENGINEERING AND ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-6">
            <h4 class="text-white font-black text-sm uppercase mb-2">BERLIN</h4>
            <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs uppercase">EUROPE CAMPUS</span>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-3 leading-relaxed">1,600 STUDENTS. SPECIALIZING IN ENERGY SYSTEMS AND ADVANCED MATERIALS SCIENCE.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-6">
            <h4 class="text-white font-black text-sm uppercase mb-2">SYDNEY</h4>
            <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs uppercase">OCEANIA CAMPUS</span>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-3 leading-relaxed">1,200 STUDENTS. FOCUSED ON MARINE SCIENCES AND CLIMATE TECHNOLOGY PROGRAMS.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-6 border-[#FFC600]/30">
            <h4 class="text-white font-black text-sm uppercase mb-2">SEA OF TRANQUILITY</h4>
            <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs uppercase">LUNAR CAMPUS</span>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase mt-3 leading-relaxed">400 STUDENTS. THE FIRST OFF-WORLD EDUCATIONAL FACILITY. ADVANCED PROGRAMS IN SPACE SCIENCES AND ENGINEERING.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- STUDENT SUCCESS STORIES -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-black border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">ALUMNI</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">
            SUCCESS <span class="text-[#FFC600]">STORIES</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="text-[#FFC600] text-4xl font-black mb-4">"</div>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
              I GREW UP IN A FISHING VILLAGE IN THE PHILIPPINES. THE EXPLORERS ACADEMY GAVE ME A FULL SCHOLARSHIP TO STUDY ATMOSPHERIC SCIENCE. TODAY, I LEAD A TERRAFORMING TEAM ON LV-223. THIS PROGRAM CHANGED EVERYTHING FOR ME AND MY FAMILY.
            </p>
            <div class="border-t border-[#1a1a1a] pt-4">
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase">MARIA SANTOS</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase">ACADEMY CLASS OF 2031 &mdash; NOW LEAD TERRAFORMING ENGINEER</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="text-[#FFC600] text-4xl font-black mb-4">"</div>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
              THE MENTORSHIP PROGRAM WAS THE DIFFERENCE. MY MENTOR AT W-Y HELPED ME SEE A PATH I NEVER THOUGHT POSSIBLE. FROM THE NAIROBI CAMPUS TO THE CYBERNETICS DIVISION IN SAN FRANCISCO, THE ACADEMY MADE IT HAPPEN.
            </p>
            <div class="border-t border-[#1a1a1a] pt-4">
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase">DR. KWAME ASANTE</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase">ACADEMY CLASS OF 2029 &mdash; NOW SYNTHETIC INTELLIGENCE RESEARCHER</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="text-[#FFC600] text-4xl font-black mb-4">"</div>
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
              AS A FIRST-GENERATION COLLEGE STUDENT FROM RURAL BRAZIL, I NEVER IMAGINED I WOULD STUDY ON THE MOON. THE LUNAR CAMPUS GAVE ME HANDS-ON EXPERIENCE WITH FTL SYSTEMS WHILE I WAS STILL A STUDENT. NOW I DESIGN THEM.
            </p>
            <div class="border-t border-[#1a1a1a] pt-4">
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase">LUCAS FERREIRA</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase">ACADEMY CLASS OF 2033 &mdash; NOW FTL PROPULSION ENGINEER</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- APPLICATION INFO -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-[#0a0a0a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">ENROLLMENT</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">
            APPLICATION <span class="text-[#FFC600]">INFORMATION</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="corp-card p-8 md:p-12">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-6 uppercase border-b border-[#FFC600]/30 pb-4">ELIGIBILITY</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-3">
                <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed status-active">AGES 14-22 AT TIME OF APPLICATION</li>
                <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed status-active">DEMONSTRATED APTITUDE IN STEM SUBJECTS</li>
                <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed status-active">FINANCIAL NEED VERIFICATION (NEED-BLIND FOR MERIT SCHOLARS)</li>
                <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed status-active">NO PRIOR CORPORATE AFFILIATION REQUIRED</li>
                <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed status-active">OPEN TO ALL EARTH AND COLONY RESIDENTS</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-6 uppercase border-b border-[#FFC600]/30 pb-4">KEY DATES</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-3">
                <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed status-active">APPLICATION WINDOW: JANUARY 1 - MARCH 31</li>
                <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed status-active">APTITUDE ASSESSMENT: APRIL - MAY</li>
                <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed status-active">ACCEPTANCE NOTIFICATIONS: JUNE 15</li>
                <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed status-active">ORIENTATION: AUGUST</li>
                <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed status-active">ACADEMIC YEAR BEGINS: SEPTEMBER 1</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="divider-yellow"></div>

          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase mb-8">
              FOR ENROLLMENT INQUIRIES, PLEASE CONTACT THE EXPLORERS ACADEMY ADMISSIONS OFFICE.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
              <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary text-sm">APPLY NOW</a>
              <a href="/sustainability/community" class="btn-secondary text-sm">COMMUNITY IMPACT</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .clip-corner {
    clip-path: polygon(8px 0, 100% 0, 100% calc(100% - 8px), calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0 100%, 0 8px);
  }
</style>
